works.description:
There are two pieces that this person has
 
been using illegally.  The first is entitled "Bird Cage" and is in the
post  
linked below.  It is an anatomical rib cage with a heart inside, flowers  

and birds around it.  The second piece is in the right side-bar of the  
blog, entitled "Page 571" and has a large anatomical heart with flowers  
growing from it.  One of them is very lightly watermarked with my business
 
name, Altered Bits.
